# @param {Integer[][]} values
# @return {Integer}
def max_spending(values)
    max_amount = 0
    day = 1
    pq = []
    values.each { |shop| pq.push(shop.pop) }
    while !pq.empty?
        pq.sort!.reverse!
        max_amount += pq.pop * day
        day += 1
        values.each_with_index do |shop, i|
            pq.push(shop.pop) unless shop.empty?
        end
    end
    max_amount
end
